<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='386000' id='t-386000'>Compassion also looks like this.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='389000' id='t-389000'>This is Jean Vanier.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='392000' id='t-392000'>Jean Vanier helped found the L'Arche communities,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='394000' id='t-394000'>which you can now find all over the world,</span>
