<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='457000' id='t-457000'>And compassion is unleashed</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='460000' id='t-460000'>in wider and wider circles</span>
