<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='533000' id='t-533000'>Now this might sound like a fanciful tale.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='536000' id='t-536000'>Some of my fellow journalists might interpret it that way.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='539000' id='t-539000'>Rachel Naomi Remen says</span>
