<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='561000' id='t-561000'>Stories like this,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='564000' id='t-564000'>signs like this,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='566000' id='t-566000'>are practical tools</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='568000' id='t-568000'>in a world longing to bring compassion</span>
