12:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='720000' id='t-720000'>Now invoking Einstein</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722000' id='t-722000'>might not seem the best way to bring compassion down to earth</span>
