<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='727000' id='t-727000'>but actually it is.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='730000' id='t-730000'>I want to show you</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='732000' id='t-732000'>the rest of this photograph,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='735000' id='t-735000'>because this photograph</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='737000' id='t-737000'>is analogous to what we do to the word &quot;compassion&quot; in our culture --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='740000' id='t-740000'>we clean it up</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='742000' id='t-742000'>and we diminish its depths and its grounding</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='745000' id='t-745000'>in life, which is messy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='747000' id='t-747000'>So in this photograph</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='749000' id='t-749000'>you see a mind looking out a window</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='751000' id='t-751000'>at what might be a cathedral -- it's not.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='753000' id='t-753000'>This is the full photograph,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='755000' id='t-755000'>and you see a middle-aged man wearing a leather jacket,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='757000' id='t-757000'>smoking a cigar.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='759000' id='t-759000'>And by the look of that paunch,</span>
