<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='763000' id='t-763000'>We put these two photographs side-by-side on our website,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='766000' id='t-766000'>and someone said, &quot;When I look at the first photo,</span>
